64
00:07:19,300 --> 00:07:20,970
Bye!

65
00:07:21,100 --> 00:07:25,700
With guns we fight on

66
00:07:34,820 --> 00:07:36,480
Attack!

67
00:07:40,590 --> 00:07:44,630
Attack! Attack!

68
00:07:44,630 --> 00:07:47,760
Attack! Attack! Attack!

69
00:08:09,280 --> 00:08:11,020
Run!

70
00:09:13,210 --> 00:09:15,980
Copy me. Breathe deeply.

71
00:09:16,680 --> 00:09:18,520
Don't you know what that means?

72
00:09:20,390 --> 00:09:22,360
Inhale deeply.

73
00:09:22,360 --> 00:09:25,620
Breathe out. Breathe in.

74
00:09:25,660 --> 00:09:27,290
Breathe out.

75
00:09:54,390 --> 00:09:56,990
Did a tear gas canister do this?

76
00:09:56,990 --> 00:09:59,220
No, a Molotov cocktail.

77
00:10:03,700 --> 00:10:06,000
Did they have to throw a vase?

78
00:10:20,680 --> 00:10:22,510
Don't touch it.

79
00:10:24,690 --> 00:10:26,820
Don't rub it. Press down on it.

80
00:10:28,590 --> 00:10:30,490
Can you manage on your own?

81
00:10:30,490 --> 00:10:32,120
Yes.

82
00:10:41,040 --> 00:10:43,630
I didn't even ask for his name.

83
