132
00:14:56,220 --> 00:14:57,930
Are you looking for someone?

133
00:14:57,930 --> 00:15:00,860
What? Oh, class of 1995...

134
00:15:00,860 --> 00:15:02,830
Who in that year?

135
00:15:02,960 --> 00:15:05,230
There are so many.

136
00:15:06,670 --> 00:15:08,830
- Han... - Jae Hyun?

137
00:15:09,100 --> 00:15:10,440
Jae Hyun.

138
00:15:10,440 --> 00:15:12,010
Someone's here for you.

139
00:15:12,010 --> 00:15:14,400
She's really pretty. A class queen.

