00:15:46,340 --> 00:15:48,610
(Law Department Student Society)

141
00:16:42,400 --> 00:16:43,800
Four years these days...

142
00:16:43,800 --> 00:16:46,270
is enough time to remodel a whole landscape.

143
00:16:46,270 --> 00:16:49,470
I'll be honest. The sentence was too tough.

144
00:16:50,270 --> 00:16:52,140
Why do you think so?

145
00:16:52,570 --> 00:16:56,270
The stock price manipulation and embezzling.

146
00:16:56,380 --> 00:16:58,910
It was all the chairman's doing.

147
00:17:00,980 --> 00:17:02,450
I'm sorry. Are you okay?

148
00:17:02,450 --> 00:17:04,520
Is this what suddenly turning frigid means?

149
00:17:04,520 --> 00:17:06,050
I apologize.

150
00:17:06,050 --> 00:17:07,520
(No jaywalking)

151
00:17:07,520 --> 00:17:09,220
Lady!

152
00:17:10,290 --> 00:17:11,990
You can't jump out like that.

153
00:17:11,990 --> 00:17:14,330
Sorry. My plastic bag tore.

154
00:17:14,330 --> 00:17:15,630
Get out of the way.

155
