195
00:18:54,800 --> 00:18:56,460
Cancel the unfair dismissal!

196
00:18:56,460 --> 00:18:58,460
- Cancel! - Cancel!

197
00:18:58,970 --> 00:19:01,800
What an eventful welcome ceremony.

198
00:19:02,400 --> 00:19:04,410
Even if it were sewage and not an egg,

199
00:19:04,410 --> 00:19:06,710
I'd have laughed like a lunatic.

200
00:19:06,710 --> 00:19:09,010
It's my first day back in society.

201
00:19:09,010 --> 00:19:11,980
Spending time behind bars is no easy feat.

202
00:19:12,310 --> 00:19:15,080
- You did well. - Not at all.

203
00:19:15,780 --> 00:19:17,590
Do you want to return to work?

204
00:19:17,590 --> 00:19:19,690
I've been away for so long that I am a bit anxious.

205
00:19:19,690 --> 00:19:21,650
Then go to the supermarket.

206
00:19:21,660 --> 00:19:23,590
I put Seo Kyung in charge,

207
00:19:23,590 --> 00:19:25,560
but I'm not sure she'll manage.

208
00:19:26,660 --> 00:19:29,500
Four years will pass in no time.

209
00:19:29,500 --> 00:19:32,430
Take the fall and hang in there for four years.

210
00:19:32,730 --> 00:19:35,470
Then I'll make you my successor.

211
00:19:38,170 --> 00:19:41,340
The women protesting down there.

212
00:19:41,340 --> 00:19:44,640
I want them out of my sight.

213
00:19:45,950 --> 00:19:49,150
You're the best at getting rid of people.

214
00:19:50,920 --> 00:19:54,250
Why do you think they call you Scissorhands?

215
00:19:55,320 --> 00:19:57,020
Yes, sir.

216
00:19:59,090 --> 00:20:00,630
Jae Hyun.

217
00:20:00,630 --> 00:20:03,560
Just because the hound brought back the hare,

218
00:20:03,560 --> 00:20:07,000
did you ever see a hunter let the hound keep it?

219
00:20:07,430 --> 00:20:10,930
A hound must eat what a hound eats.

220
00:20:11,110 --> 00:20:13,970
If it wants the hare,

221
00:20:14,480 --> 00:20:17,440
wouldn't the hunter get angry?

222
00:20:18,010 --> 00:20:19,680
Yes.

223
00:20:21,720 --> 00:20:24,380
You don't have to work right away.

224
00:20:25,150 --> 00:20:27,250
You need to play some.

225
00:20:27,250 --> 00:20:28,960
You always worked,

226
00:20:28,960 --> 00:20:31,890
so did you forget how to play?

227
00:20:33,260 --> 00:20:35,990
I'm not sure what to do, but I'll give it a go.

228
00:20:36,060 --> 00:20:39,530
I'm a pretty quick learner.

229
00:20:42,670 --> 00:20:48,740
Let's try living like a rock

230
