We will not fall for any trick or lure

232
00:21:01,160 --> 00:21:07,520
Let's try living like a rock

233
00:21:08,560 --> 00:21:10,260
Hey, Young Min.

234
00:21:10,560 --> 00:21:13,430
Shall I bring something tasty this weekend?

235
00:21:15,740 --> 00:21:18,670
(Murderous Company)

236
00:21:18,670 --> 00:21:21,400
Young Min, sorry. I'll call you back.

237
00:21:26,450 --> 00:21:28,020
Thank you.

238
00:21:28,020 --> 00:21:29,780
Not at all.

239
00:21:29,950 --> 00:21:32,790
I'll stick this together and bring it back.

240
00:21:32,790 --> 00:21:36,690
Don't bother. I should do that. This is about my son.

241
00:21:36,690 --> 00:21:38,690
I have a son too.

242
00:21:38,690 --> 00:21:41,160
So I want to help you.

243
00:21:41,700 --> 00:21:44,130
They're such bad people.

244
00:21:46,930 --> 00:21:48,840
What do the youth do to play?

245
00:21:48,840 --> 00:21:52,270
They play games or drink alcohol.

246
00:21:52,570 --> 00:21:55,010
Guys go and play billiards.

247
00:21:55,010 --> 00:21:57,780
You say the landscape gets remodelled in four years,

248
00:21:57,780 --> 00:21:59,640
so why hasn't that changed?

249
00:22:00,350 --> 00:22:03,480
I don't know. How about a movie?

250
00:22:03,480 --> 00:22:05,280
Some nice ones are out.

251
00:22:05,820 --> 00:22:07,550
I don't like that.

252
00:22:08,160 --> 00:22:09,920
Things like movies.

