Do you want "Love Letter" too?

290
00:25:49,580 --> 00:25:51,650
You placed an order first.

291
00:25:51,650 --> 00:25:53,350
Why are you just leaving?

292
00:25:53,350 --> 00:25:54,920
You can have it.

293
00:25:54,920 --> 00:25:57,780
You ordered it because you want to watch.

294
00:25:57,780 --> 00:26:00,480
I'd feel bad to keep it for myself.

295
00:26:00,720 --> 00:26:03,060
- Then what? - Let's watch together.

296
00:26:03,060 --> 00:26:04,490
Dampopo said that...

297
00:26:04,490 --> 00:26:07,360
the video will be too grainy if he makes another copy.

298
00:26:07,360 --> 00:26:10,130
- Or if you watch it too much. - Forget it.

299
00:26:11,200 --> 00:26:13,030
I won't tell anyone.

300
00:26:13,030 --> 00:26:15,400
No one would believe me anyway.

301
00:26:15,400 --> 00:26:16,840
Who'd believe that...

302
00:26:16,840 --> 00:26:19,740
a hardcore protester watches sad Japanese movies?

303
00:26:19,740 --> 00:26:22,340
Don't you speak Korean? I said forget it.

304
00:26:46,900 --> 00:26:49,800
I want to watch "Love Letter" with you.

